HEALTH_AND_NUTRITION.title: Community Health and Nutrition Services
HEALTH_AND_NUTRITION.description: Provision of basic health services, nutrition monitoring, and maternal and child health programs at the barangay level.

FAMILY_PLANNING.title: Family Planning and Reproductive Health Program
FAMILY_PLANNING.description: Access to family planning information, counseling, and contraceptive services to promote responsible parenthood.

SANITATION_UPGRADE.description: Provision and upgrading of household toilets and sanitation facilities to reduce health risks.

SOLID_WASTE_MANAGEMENT.title: Solid Waste Segregation and Management Program
SOLID_WASTE_MANAGEMENT.description: Barangay-wide waste segregation and Materials Recovery Facility strengthening.

URBAN_GARDENING.title: Urban Gardening and Food Security Program
URBAN_GARDENING.description: Promotion of household and community gardens to improve food security.

LIVELIHOOD_TRAINING.title: Livelihood Skills Training Program
LIVELIHOOD_TRAINING.description: Skills development and livelihood training to support household income generation.
